snippet.title: Finding a Unit Vector, Ex 1
snippet.description: Thanks to all of you who support me on Patreon. You da real mvps!   $1 per month helps!! :)  https://www.patreon.com/patrickjmt !! Finding a Unit Vector, Ex 1.  In this video I discuss the idea of a unit vector and show how to find it (divide the vector by its magnitude!).
